<!--pages/open/open.wxml-->
<view class="container">
  <view class="result-wrapper">
    <view class="result-header">
      <text class="result-title">恭喜你！获得店家{{boxId}}精心埋藏的宝藏</text>
      <view class='result-value'>
        <image class="icon" src="/static/images/logo-active.png"></image>
        <text class="font">价值100元</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="result-content">
      <image class="ent-img" src="/static/images/logo/img02.jpg"></image>
      <text class="story-content">【江湖传言】据说发现了必胜客老板私藏的私房钱，为了不被发现，他偷偷藏到了3个地方。快去寻找吧。。。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="result-foot">
      <button class="open-btn" type="primary" bind:tap="handleOpen">开启</button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>